com.mattrader.common

Class SessionDBCom

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mattrader.common.SessionDBCom

  • public class SessionDBCom
extends java.lang.Object
    A little in memory database, it will keep track of prices and book levels that happens while the ticker has been subscribed to Darwin. Practically this database store informations for a TickerCom that has open a dataFeed service. Methods for querying data are provided. Every operation should be thread safe and a couple of locks are involved.

    The session has a maximum size, see MTClientBaseCom.defaultSessionBuffer(int), and data will be truncated if this limit is overflowed by more than 10%. Data may also be discarded by the mean of a call to flush()
